entries.entry: Today I learned that men in fact do not know what they are talking about.

I learned more about JavaScript and their functions. I had recently looked at functions and things change all the time. We also talked about the big arrow functions. I'm feeling more comfortable with it.
We presented our projects today and that was fun yet a disaster because we didn't finish our project.
Today we learned about manipulating the DOM and how we would be making a lot of home page with javascript instead of html.
